  "title": "Designer (Electrical)",
  "description": "<p>We are now looking for fresh or experienced Electrical Designer to join our multi-disciplinary team and you will have opportunity to work on a variety of challenging design and construction supervision projects.<br /></p><p><strong>Requirement :</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma in Electrical Engineering or equivalent with experience in design of Building Electrical Services</li><li>Fresh graduate or 1-2 years working experience in the relevant field.</li><li>Autocad and Revit skill is essential</li><li>Familiar with all the Electrical Code of Practice</li><li>Good fundamental electrical engineering knowledge, good analytical, interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Familiar with Dialux would be advantages</li></ul><p><strong>Your responsibilities include:</strong></p><ul><li>Produce quality Electrical Tender drawings with Autocad or Revit on time</li><li>Prepare submission for Substation, TFCC and EVC</li></ul>",
